oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Tintype of Napoleon Bonaparte Andrews
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Napoleon Bonaparte Andrews tintype. He was born on January 6, 1844, in Virginia, and died October 14, 1900 in Monterey, Putnam County, Tennessee. The image is from New Middleton, Smith County, Tennessee.
oai_dc:dc.dc:source: Fort Negley, Nashville, Davidson County, Tennessee
